One aspect of this sort of approach may be to more thoroughly examine 
the fitness space around a given species. The current mechanism of 
having many species potentially dilutes the ability to search any one 
species. Having said that, sharpneat disables the standard culling of 
stalled species for the best species,  hence a stalled dominant species 
should be spawning off side-species anyway.


